        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://lessig.org/blog/2008/02/20_minutes_or_so_on_why_i_am_4.html">20 minutes or so on why I am 4Barack (Lessig Blog)</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Reasoned video from Lawrence Lessig on why he supports Obama.  If you&#8217;re worried that Obama is all-sizzle-no-steak or cult-of-personality, this is worth watching.</p>

<p>(As an aside, I see from the comments that noted raging fuckwit Marc Perkel is anti-Obama. I consider that another positive.)</p>

