<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/feb/21/">&#x27a0;</a> February 21, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Second Life Barack Obama meetup</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/398321980/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Second Life Barack Obama meetup" src="http://farm1.static.flickr.com/128/398321980_ce18a4964b_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>Now that I've got a suitably powerful computer, I've finally had a chance to poke at Second Life.</p>

<p>It's not living up to the hype by any stretch, though it is fascinating.  While looking for something to do, I &quot;transported&quot; into this Barack Obama &quot;meetup&quot;, which was guarded over by a stormtrooper.  Obviously.</p>
        </p>

